{"tid":2478723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"營救理大案家長車司機被加控妨礙司法公正 保釋金大幅提升至十萬 需每日警署報到","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:44:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"18a2334da395e1f697b920a6879735b2cffb4661","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14840&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=19e569f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #轉介文件<br />\n👤梁(23) #1120紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月20日，在尖沙咀不遠處的暢通道南（地圖顯示現場為理工大學香港專上學院對開）涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：妨礙司法公正<br />\n(稍後補上)<br />\n===============<br />\n‼️控方表示有新增控罪，並申請撤銷被告擔保‼️<br />\n<br />\n✅法庭拒絕控方撤銷被告擔保的申請，唯被告需要遵守新修訂的保釋的條件✅<br />\n-保釋金提升至$100,000<br />\n-每天到警署報到<br />\n-其他條件依舊<br />\n<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年4月27日14:30在區域法院進行答辯程序，聆訊會用中文進行。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示會保留不在場證據。"},{"pid":"cce1c6230cc570c7245caa0b594885920e8ca353","tid":2478723,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b85ba73eacff595cfadfe007e97ce5131d3e7","tid":2478723,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"5b2c6dc7f8689876393b8721cf37afde28f2662c","tid":2478723,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb719b37b8a5ef729c1fa9e08b32518c0ac09c8","tid":2478723,"uid":74282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f7c39d417f812dca21ef6960779e245583c7b6","tid":2478723,"uid":157532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf41b99ad6a04a3f0929742c9b0ecc14e671d508","tid":2478723,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5295666d69a18901abf9c66a1f27bdab243b5c","tid":2478723,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b965acf1253c85e97ee7e8af9dcd87c9c8641511","tid":2478723,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"危駕老妨都想唔比人保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb632fa7dd3a313f63787c7960316d4ad6d2312","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #轉介文件<br />\n👤陳(32) #1118紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月18日，在紅磡繞道近理工大學李兆基樓涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛客貨車。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：妨礙司法公正<br />\n================<br />\n辯方表示不反對控罪的修訂，亦保留不在場證據。<br />\n<br />\n✅控方撤回撤銷擔保的申請✅<br />\n<br />\n法庭批准被告繼續保釋，唯需遵守更嚴格的保釋條件：<br />\n-保釋金需提升至$100,000<br />\n-每天到警署報到<br />\n-若地址更改需24小時前通知警署<br />\n-其他條件依舊<br />\n<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年4月27日14:30在區域法院進行答辯程序，聆訊會用中文進行。"},{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},{"pid":"2142cc13e37af178a447efc2baad5a45a0ad4ed2","tid":2478723,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"算係咁拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f295054dc14c94fa964387d2baa85f9515c55f3b","tid":2478723,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"好彩比保"},{"pid":"cf0d97ce3a23cd15061d708d60d4b8793733ff2c","tid":2478723,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2acd214b9c090b53b180ce42a05ec104e92525","tid":2478723,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"依個官一時時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd073900592e9e0a7d04e62b8a22ee2d08aa896","tid":2478723,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"保到就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286a3f66963fb3c61f89e85b5cf0d8989508cc29","tid":2478723,"uid":93615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fe78af10cb390024b0cbf94a25e173e158e605","tid":2478723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"點撚樣妨礙司法公正呀又？"},{"pid":"07cb2b7293f5fb2d81b5a49c4447d3d379fd608c","tid":2478723,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f34c44b0fafcf3205298bf0a3f9f931a9df284","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fe78af10cb390024b0cbf94a25e173e158e605","tid":2478723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"點撚樣妨礙司法公正呀又？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"呼吸都係妨礙司法公正"},{"pid":"a800e351a6ffd3266cc0fed925a2ba7f442e621e","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"據了解，案發時有車停泊在連接理工大學的一條水渠外，有人從渠底出來並登上汽車。警員嘗試截停查問時車子突然開動，撞到警員的大腿。此外，涉案時亦有汽車停泊在理大校舍外，接載從校舍游繩而下的人士。"},{"pid":"4cfd2f80b5efc042471326cb38278ea6b465b35a","tid":2478723,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"9a73c6dd8d5908a16d35cd5338431b8e31d0b508","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"前年11月理大圍城期間，有被圍示威者分別爬渠及從校園游繩逃走，並由義載司機接走。警方去年起訴兩名疑於現場附近駕駛「家長車」的司機，控以危險駕駛罪，案件今於九龍城裁判法院再訊。控方今加控兩人妨礙司法公正罪，並向法庭申請撤銷保釋。最終主任裁判官嚴舜儀准許兩人繼續保釋，但將原本1,000元的保釋金大幅增加至現金10萬元，並須每日向警署報到。兩被告一度還柙，等候籌措保釋金。案件押後至本月27日於區域法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n控方今加控兩人一項妨礙司法公正罪，指他們同日連同其他人意圖作出傾向協助其他人逃避逮捕的作為，而他知道其他人會被香港警務處逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n法庭除了增加擔保金額，另將向警署報到的日數增至每周7天。至於宵禁及不准離港的保釋條件則維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/QT2P7IHQAJHVZIZ3CEP3DS7SYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FQT2P7IHQAJHVZIZ3CEP3DS7SYE%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6183abb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FQT2P7IHQAJHVZIZ3CEP3DS7SYE%2F&h=f3e07e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/QT2P7IHQAJHVZIZ3CEP3DS7SYE/</a>"},{"pid":"4542519e4285d78092c8623c99e32608904e05be","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"警方於 2019 年 11 月包圍理工大學，網民發起營救行動。兩名「家長車」司機分別被指接載從渠口及游繩離開理大的示威者，期間一架車輛碰觸到一名警員，兩名司機原被控一項危險駕駛。案件今（7 日）在九龍城裁判法院再提堂，兩人遭加控妨礙司法公正罪，案件轉介區域法院，於 4 月 27 日再訊。主任裁判官嚴舜儀批准兩人繼續保釋，但增添更嚴格保釋條件，包括每日到警署報到、保釋金額增至 10 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n兩人今日各遭加控一項妨礙司法公正罪，指梁及陳分別於 2019 年 11 月 20 及 18 日，在香港連同其他人意圖妨害司法公正，而作出一連串妨礙司法公正傾向的作為，即意圖協助其他人逃避逮捕的行為，而明知該人會被香港警務處逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解被告當時將車駛至連接理大的渠口位，遭警方截停時，車上有一名乘客。被告聲稱兩人去吃飯，警員要求他停車及搜車，被告試圖駕車逃走，期間車輛觸碰到警員大腿；另一被告則被指接載游繩離開理大的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%BB%8A-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95-%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A7%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3-%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E9%87%91%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3-10-%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2590%258D-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%25A7%2595-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3-10-%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=8bdd590d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2590%258D-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%25A7%2595-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3-10-%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&h=d4fee601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%BB%8A-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95-%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A7%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3-%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E9%87%91%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3-10-%E8%90%AC/</a>"},{"pid":"a02cf7b597152d1d889dc695ef91b434c8ced487","tid":2478723,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}